Backup and Restore:
-------------------

kubectl get pods -A -o yaml > hdfcproject.yaml

describe etcd 

kubectl describe pod etcd-k-m -n kube-system

to take a backup,
cd /var/lib/etcd/
and take backup of member dir


Backup 

etcdctl snaphot save --endpoint=127.0.0.1:2379 --cacert=/etc/kubernetes/pki/etcd/ca.crt --cert=/etc/kubernetes/pki/etcd/server.crt --key=/etc/kubernetes/pki/etcd/server.key /tmp/etcd.db


Restore:

etcdctl snapshot restore --data-dir /var/lib/etcd-backup /tmp/etcd.db

kubectl restart kubelet